    "(RQ4) How robust is the semantics of aligned visual features to visual variations?",
    "These questions are investigated in detail in Section 5.2.",
    "Detailed experiment settings are provided in Appendix D.",
    "The evaluation results across different LVLM architectures and model scales are presented in Table 1.",
    "Despite their impressive performance demonstrated on complex visual tasks, these models exhibit surprising vulnerability to simple visual variations, resulting in significantly degraded performance across basic visual tasks."
